  <entry>
    <title>生日小诗</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2021/09/17/%E6%96%87%E5%AD%A6/happy%20birthday/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2021/09/17/%E6%96%87%E5%AD%A6/happy%20birthday/</id>
    <published>2021-09-17T12:26:36.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-09-17T12:47:42.737Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><iframe frameborder="no" border="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" width="98%" height="86" src="//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=527620034&auto=1&height=66"></iframe>生日写了一首小诗仿写了我超喜欢的《借我》也希望我的新的一岁，所求皆如愿，所行化坦途，多喜乐，长安宁。<p><strong><font face="方正FW童趣POP体 简" color="#F17C67" size="6">借我</font></strong> - <strong><font face="方正FW童趣POP体 简" size="4">小言</font></strong><br>借我一个少年，<br>借我远方，<br>借我天真与无邪。<br>借我倔强如过往，<br>借我犹豫不决的残忍，<br>借我怯弱但勇往直前。<br>借我浓情的问候和素淡的心，<br>借我不偏移的爱。<br>借我缄默的善良，<br>借我慵懒的忧郁和鲁莽的坚持。<br>借我稚嫩到成熟的徘徊，<br>借我无话不说的午夜。<br>借我一个盛夏吧！<br>就算你说这已是秋天。</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
